				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Happy to see this back up! The rewrite fixes my main problem with the original, that the epitaph dragged for too long, and it's all-around more punchy. I like it.</p> <blockquote> <p>Based on Ortothan beliefs of the divine being agender or genderfluid in nature, these are presumably referring to the same subject.</p> </blockquote> <p>I also still love this, again probably because this was news to me as someone who hasn't read much Hytoth stuff.</p> 
				 	]]>
